A summer I’ll never forget.. 4 national parks, 2500+ miles, and a lifetime of memories. Thankful for this one to show me a world I never knew..

Happy birthday to the woman of my dreams. Not only have you pushed me to be a better man, you’ve shown me what it’s like to be loved day in and day out. You’ve taken me to places I’d never imagine seeing in my lifetime, and you push me past my comfort zone to learn new things. From day one, you’ve been my rock, my mentor, and my idol.
